<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>NIO - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/nio/</link><description>NIO - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/nio/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Netty网络框架</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/netty/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/netty/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="netty网络框架">Netty网络框架</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Netty基于NIO多路复用和事件驱动模型，通过EventLoop处理IO事件，通过ChannelPipeline串联业务处理器，通过ByteBuf实现高效内存管理，是构建高性能网络服务的首选框架。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="netty通过eventloop线程模型处理io通过channelpipeline串联处理器通过bytebuf管理内存实现高并发低延迟网络通信">Netty通过EventLoop线程模型处理IO，通过ChannelPipeline串联处理器，通过ByteBuf管理内存，实现高并发低延迟网络通信</h2>
<h3 id="核心组件eventloopchannelpipelinebytebuf">核心组件：EventLoop、Channel、Pipeline、ByteBuf</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>组件</th>
          <th>职责</th>
          <th>类比</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>EventLoop</td>
          <td>IO事件循环处理</td>
          <td>NIO中的Selector + 线程</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Channel</td>
          <td>网络连接抽象</td>
          <td>SocketChannel</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ChannelPipeline</td>
          <td>处理器责任链</td>
          <td>Filter链/拦截器链</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ChannelHandler</td>
          <td>具体处理器</td>
          <td>Servlet/Controller</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ByteBuf</td>
          <td>字节缓冲区</td>
          <td>NIO ByteBuffer的增强版</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Bootstrap</td>
          <td>启动辅助类</td>
          <td>Spring ApplicationContext</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Netty服务端线程模型：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Boss Group（通常1个线程）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── 监听端口，accept新连接
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      将新Channel注册到Worker Group的某个EventLoop
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Worker Group（N个EventLoop线程，通常CPU核数*2）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── EventLoop-1: 管理 Channel-1, Channel-5, Channel-9...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── EventLoop-2: 管理 Channel-2, Channel-6, Channel-10...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── EventLoop-N: 管理 Channel-N...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  每个EventLoop绑定一个Selector，处理分配给它的所有Channel的IO事件</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
